<pb ed="T" id="T14.0581.0965a" n="0965a"/>
<lb n="0965a01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0965a02"/><head type="no">No. 581</head>
<lb n="0965a03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead>佛說八師經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0965a04"/>
<lb n="0965a05"/><byline type="Translator">吳月支<note n="0965001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔國〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0965001"><lem>國</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0965002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">居士＝優婆塞【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">居士＝優婆塞【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965002"><lem>居士</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">優婆塞</rdg></app>支謙譯</byline>
<lb n="0965a06"/><div1 type="jing"><p>聞如是。一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。時
<lb n="0965a07"/>有梵志。名曰<note n="0965003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耶句＝邪旬【宋】【宮】，耶旬【元】【明】</note><note n="0965003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耶句＝邪旬【宋】【宮】，＝耶旬【元】【明】</note><app n="0965003"><lem>耶句</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">邪旬</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">耶旬</rdg></app>。來詣佛所。阿難白佛言。
<lb n="0965a08"/>有異學梵志。今來在外。欲<note n="0965004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">咨＝資【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">咨＝資【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965004"><lem>咨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">資</rdg></app>所疑。天尊曰
<lb n="0965a09"/>現之。梵志乃進。稽首佛足。天尊曰就座。梵
<lb n="0965a10"/>志就座。須臾退坐曰。吾聞佛道厥義弘深。汪
<lb n="0965a11"/>洋無涯。靡不成就。<note n="0965005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">靡＝無【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">靡＝無【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965005"><lem>靡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">無</rdg></app>不度生。巍巍堂堂。
<lb n="0965a12"/>猶星中月。神智妙達。眾聖中王。諸天所不
<lb n="0965a13"/><note n="0965006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">逮＝及【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">逮＝及【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965006"><lem>逮</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">及</rdg></app>。黎民所不聞。願開盲冥。釋其愚癡。所
<lb n="0965a14"/>事何師。以致斯尊。天尊<note n="0965007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔歎〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔歎〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965007"><lem>歎</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>曰。快哉斯問。開
<lb n="0965a15"/>發大行。吾前世師。其名難數。吾今自然神
<lb n="0965a16"/><note n="0965008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耀＝曜【宮】</note><app n="0965008"><lem>耀</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">曜</rdg></app>得道。非有師也。然有八師。從明得<note n="0965009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之＋（佛言一謂兇暴殘殺物命或為怨家所見）【宮】</note><app n="0965009"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">之佛言一謂兇暴殘殺物命或為怨家所見</rdg></app>
<lb n="0965a17"/><note n="0965010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">刑＝形【宮】</note><app n="0965010"><lem>刑</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">形</rdg></app>戮。或為王法。所見誅治。滅及門族。死
<lb n="0965a18"/>入地獄。燒煮搒掠萬毒皆更。求死不得。罪
<lb n="0965a19"/>竟乃出。或為餓鬼。或為畜生。屠割剝裂。死
<lb n="0965a20"/>輒更<note n="0965011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">刃＝生【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">刃＝生【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965011"><lem>刃</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">生</rdg></app>。魂神展轉。更相殘賊。吾見殺者。
<lb n="0965a21"/>其罪如此。不敢復殺。是吾一師。佛時頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0965a22"/><lg><l>殺者心不仁</l><l>強弱相<note n="0965012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">傷殘＝殘傷【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">傷殘＝殘傷【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965012"><lem>傷殘</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">殘傷</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0965a23"/><l>殺<note n="0965013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＝主【宮】</note><app n="0965013"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">主</rdg></app>當過生</l><l>結積累劫怨</l>
<lb n="0965a24"/><l>受罪短命死</l><l>驚<note n="0965014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怖＝怛【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">怖＝怛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965014"><lem>怖</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">怛</rdg></app>遭暴患</l>
<lb n="0965a25"/><l>吾用畏是故</l><l>慈<note n="0965015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">心＝行【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心＝行【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965015"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">行</rdg></app>伏魔宮</l></lg>
<lb n="0965a26"/><p>佛言。二謂盜竊。強劫人財。或為財主。刀杖
<lb n="0965a27"/>加刑。應時瓦解。或為王法。收繫著獄。<note n="0965016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拷＝考【宋】【明】【宮】，者【元】</note><note n="0965016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拷＝考【宋】【明】【宮】，＝者【元】</note><app n="0965016"><lem>拷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">考</rdg><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">者</rdg></app>掠
<lb n="0965a28"/>榜笞。五毒並至。戮之都市。<note n="0965017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">宗門＝門族【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">宗門＝門族【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965017"><lem>宗門</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">門族</rdg></app>灰滅。死
<lb n="0965a29"/>入地獄。以手捧火。洋銅沃口。求死不得。罪
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0581.0965b" n="0965b"/>
<lb n="0965b01"/>竟乃出。當為餓鬼。意欲飲水。水化為膿。所
<lb n="0965b02"/>欲食物。物化成炭。身常負重。眾惱自隨。或
<lb n="0965b03"/>為畜生。死輒更刃。以肉供人。償其宿債。吾
<lb n="0965b04"/>見盜者。其罪如此。不敢復盜。是吾二師。佛
<lb n="0965b05"/>時頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0965b06"/><lg><l>盜者不與取</l><l>劫竊人財寶</l>
<lb n="0965b07"/><l>亡者無多少</l><l>忿恚<note n="0965018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">懷憂＝愁毒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">懷憂＝愁毒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965018"><lem>懷憂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">愁毒</rdg></app>惱</l>
<lb n="0965b08"/><l>死受六畜<note n="0965019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">身＝形【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">身＝形【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965019"><lem>身</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">形</rdg></app></l><l>償其宿債負</l>
<lb n="0965b09"/><l>吾用畏是故</l><l>棄<note n="0965020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">家行學道＝國施財寶【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">家行學道＝國施財寶【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965020"><lem>家行學道</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">國施財寶</rdg></app></l></lg>
<lb n="0965b10"/><p>佛言。三謂邪婬。犯人婦女。或為夫主。邊人
<lb n="0965b11"/>所知。臨時得殃。刀杖加<note n="0965021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">刑＝形【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0965021"><lem>刑</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">形</rdg></app>。<note n="0965022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（首體分離禍及門族）＋或【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（首體分離禍及門族）＋或【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965022"><lem>或</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">首體分離禍及門族或</rdg></app>為王法。收
<lb n="0965b12"/><note n="0965023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">繫＝捕【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">繫＝捕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965023"><lem>繫</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">捕</rdg></app>著獄。酷毒掠治。<note n="0965024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">戮之都市＝身自當辜【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">戮之都市＝身自當辜【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965024"><lem>戮之都市</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">身自當辜</rdg></app>。死入地獄。
<lb n="0965b13"/>臥之鐵床。或抱銅柱。獄鬼然火。以燒其身。
<lb n="0965b14"/>地獄罪畢。當更畜生。若<note n="0965025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">復＝後【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復＝後【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965025"><lem>復</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">後</rdg></app>為人。閨門婬亂。
<lb n="0965b15"/>違佛遠法。不親賢眾。常懷恐怖。多危少安。
<lb n="0965b16"/>吾見是故。不敢邪婬。是吾三師。佛時頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0965b17"/><lg><l>婬為不淨行</l><l>迷惑失<note n="0965026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">正＝生【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">正＝生【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965026"><lem>正</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">生</rdg></app>道</l>
<lb n="0965b18"/><l><note n="0965027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">精神＝形銷【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">精神＝形銷【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965027"><lem>精神</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">形銷</rdg></app>魂魄<note n="0965028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">馳＝離【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">馳＝離【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965028"><lem>馳</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">離</rdg></app></l><l>傷命而早夭</l>
<lb n="0965b19"/><l>受罪頑癡荒</l><l>死復墮惡道</l>
<lb n="0965b20"/><l><note n="0965029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吾用畏是故＝故吾妻子施【宮】</note><app n="0965029"><lem>吾用畏是故</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">故吾妻子施</rdg></app></l><l>棄家樂<note n="0965030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">林＝山【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">林＝山【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965030"><lem>林</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">山</rdg></app>藪</l></lg>
<lb n="0965b21"/><p>佛言。四謂<note n="0965031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惡口兩舌＝兩舌惡口【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惡口兩舌＝兩舌惡口【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965031"><lem>惡口兩舌</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">兩舌惡口</rdg></app>妄言綺語。譖入無罪。
<lb n="0965b22"/><note n="0965032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謗毀＝毀謗【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">謗毀＝毀謗【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965032"><lem>謗毀</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">毀謗</rdg></app>三尊。舌致捶杖。亦致滅門。死<note n="0965033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入＝人【宋】</note><app n="0965033"><lem>入</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">人</rdg></app>地
<lb n="0965b23"/>獄。獄中鬼神。拔出其舌。以牛犁之。洋銅灌
<lb n="0965b24"/>口。求死不得。罪畢乃出。當為畜生。<note n="0965034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&M010527;＝常【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&M010527;＝常【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965034"><lem>&M010527;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">常</rdg></app>食草
<lb n="0965b25"/>棘。若後為人。言不見信。口中&M010527;臭。多<note n="0965035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">逢譖＝被誹【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">逢譖＝被誹【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965035"><lem>逢
<lb n="0965b26"/>譖</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">被誹</rdg></app>謗。罵詈之聲。臥輒惡夢。有口不<note n="0965036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔能〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔能〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965036"><lem>能</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>得含
<lb n="0965b27"/>佛經之至味。吾見是故。不敢惡口。是吾四
<lb n="0965b28"/>師。佛時頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0965b29"/><lg><l>欺者<note n="0965037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">有＝犯【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有＝犯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965037"><lem>有</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">犯</rdg></app>四過</l><l>讒&CB00126;傷<note n="0965038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">良貞＝貞賢【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">良貞＝貞賢【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965038"><lem>良貞</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">貞賢</rdg></app></l>
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0581.0965c" n="0965c"/>
<lb n="0965c01"/><l>受罪癡聾盲</l><l>蹇吃口臭腥</l>
<lb n="0965c02"/><l><note n="0965039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">癡狂＝瘖&CB00484;【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">癡狂＝瘖&CB00484;【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965039"><lem>癡狂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">瘖&CB00484;</rdg></app>不能言</l><l>死入拔舌<note n="0965040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囹＝犁【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囹＝犁【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965040"><lem>囹</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">犁</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0965c03"/><l>吾修四淨口</l><l>自致八音聲</l></lg>
<lb n="0965c04"/><p>佛言。五謂嗜酒。酒為毒氣。主成<note n="0965041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸＝眾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諸＝眾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965041"><lem>諸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">眾</rdg></app>惡。王
<lb n="0965c05"/>道毀<note n="0965042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">仁澤滅＝蘀賊【宮】</note><app n="0965042"><lem>仁澤滅</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">蘀賊</rdg></app>。臣慢上<note n="0965043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忠敬朽父失禮＝不忠不敬於父禮亡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忠敬朽父失禮＝不忠不敬於父禮亡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965043"><lem>忠。敬朽父。失禮</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">不忠不敬於父禮亡</rdg></app>母。
<lb n="0965c06"/>失慈子。凶<note n="0965044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">逆＝勃【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">逆＝勃【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965044"><lem>逆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">勃</rdg></app>孝道。敗夫失信。婦奢婬。九族
<lb n="0965c07"/>諍財產耗。<note n="0965045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">亡國危＝危國亡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">亡國危＝危國亡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965045"><lem>亡國危</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">危國亡</rdg></app>身。無不由<note n="0965046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之＝酒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之＝酒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965046"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">酒</rdg></app>。酒之亂
<lb n="0965c08"/>道三十有六。吾見是故。<note n="0965047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">絕酒不飲＝不敢飲酒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">絕酒不飲＝不敢飲酒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965047"><lem>絕酒不飲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">不敢飲酒</rdg></app>。是吾五
<lb n="0965c09"/>師。佛時頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0965c10"/><lg><l>醉者為不孝</l><l>怨禍從內生</l>
<lb n="0965c11"/><l>迷惑清高士</l><l>亂德敗淑<note n="0965048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">貞＝真【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">貞＝真【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965048"><lem>貞</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">真</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0965c12"/><l><note n="0965049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吾故＝故吾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吾故＝故吾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965049"><lem>吾故</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">故吾</rdg></app>不飲酒</l><l>慈心濟群生</l>
<lb n="0965c13"/><l>淨慧度八難</l><l>自致覺道成</l></lg>
<lb n="0965c14"/><p>佛言。六謂年老。夫老之為苦。頭白齒落。目
<lb n="0965c15"/>視<note n="0965050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02884;&CB02884;＝茫茫【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB02884;&CB02884;＝茫茫【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965050"><lem>&CB02884;&CB02884;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">茫茫</rdg></app>。耳聽不聰。盛去衰至。皮緩面皺。百
<lb n="0965c16"/>節痛疼。行步苦極。坐起呻吟。憂悲<note n="0965051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惱苦＝心惱【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惱苦＝心惱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965051"><lem>惱苦</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">心惱</rdg></app>。識
<lb n="0965c17"/>神轉滅。便旋即<note n="0965052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忘＝亡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忘＝亡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965052"><lem>忘</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">亡</rdg></app>。命日促盡。言之流涕。
<lb n="0965c18"/>吾見無常。災變如斯。故行求道。不欲更之。
<lb n="0965c19"/>是吾六師。佛時頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0965c20"/><lg><l>吾念世無常</l><l>人生要當老</l>
<lb n="0965c21"/><l>盛去日衰羸</l><l>形枯而白首</l>
<lb n="0965c22"/><l>憂勞百病生</l><l>坐起愁痛惱</l>
<lb n="0965c23"/><l>吾用畏是故</l><l>棄<note n="0965053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">家行學＝國行求【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">家行學＝國行求【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965053"><lem>家行學</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">國行求</rdg></app>道</l></lg>
<lb n="0965c24"/><p>佛言。七謂病瘦。肉盡骨立。百節皆痛。猶被杖
<lb n="0965c25"/>楚。四大進退。手足不<note n="0965054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">任＝隨【三】【宮】</note><note n="0965054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">任＝隨【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0965054"><lem>任</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">隨</rdg></app>。氣力虛竭。坐臥
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0581.0966a" n="0966a"/>
<lb n="0966a01"/>須人。口燥脣燋。筋斷鼻<note n="0966001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">坼＝烢【宋】【明】</note><app n="0966001"><lem>坼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】" resp="Taisho">烢</rdg></app>。目不見色。耳不
<lb n="0966a02"/>聞音。不淨流出。身臥其上。心懷苦惱。言輒
<lb n="0966a03"/>悲哀。今&CB00418;世人。年盛力壯。華邑暐曄。福盡
<lb n="0966a04"/>罪至。無常百變。吾&CB00418;斯患。故行求道。不欲
<lb n="0966a05"/>更之。是吾七師。佛時頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0966a06"/><lg><l>念人<note n="0966002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">衰＝哀【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0966002"><lem>衰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">哀</rdg></app>老時</l><l>百病同時生</l>
<lb n="0966a07"/><l>水<note n="0966003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">消＝銷【三】【宮】</note><note n="0966003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">消＝銷【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0966003"><lem>消</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">銷</rdg></app>而火滅</l><l>刀風解其形</l>
<lb n="0966a08"/><l>骨離筋脈<note n="0966004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">絕＝斷【三】【宮】</note><note n="0966004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">絕＝斷【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0966004"><lem>絕</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">斷</rdg></app></l><l>大命要當傾</l>
<lb n="0966a09"/><l>吾用畏是故</l><l>求道願不生</l></lg>
<lb n="0966a10"/><p>佛言。八謂人死。四百四病。同時俱作。四大
<lb n="0966a11"/>欲散。魂神不安。風去<note n="0966005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">息＝氣【三】【宮】</note><note n="0966005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">息＝氣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0966005"><lem>息</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">氣</rdg></app>絕。火滅身冷。風
<lb n="0966a12"/>先火次。魂靈去矣。身體<note n="0966006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">挺＝侹【三】【宮】</note><note n="0966006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">挺＝侹【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0966006"><lem>挺</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">侹</rdg></app>直。無所復知。
<lb n="0966a13"/>旬日之間。肉壞血流。<note n="0966007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00167;脹＝&CB00955;膿【三】【宮】</note><note n="0966007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00167;脹＝&CB00955;膿【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0966007"><lem>&CB00167;脹</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&CB00955;膿</rdg></app>爛臭。無一可取。
<lb n="0966a14"/>身中有蟲。還食其肉。筋脈爛盡。骨節解散。
<lb n="0966a15"/>髑髏異處。脊脅肩臂。&CB00170;脛足指。各自異處。
<lb n="0966a16"/>飛鳥走獸。<note n="0966008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">競＝兢【明】</note><app n="0966008"><lem>競</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">兢</rdg></app>來食之。天龍鬼神。帝王人民。
<lb n="0966a17"/>貧富貴賤。無免<note n="0966009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此＝斯【三】【宮】</note><note n="0966009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此＝斯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0966009"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">斯</rdg></app>患。吾見斯變。故行求道。
<lb n="0966a18"/>不欲更之。是吾八師。佛時頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0966a19"/><lg><l><note n="0966010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">我惟＝惟念【三】【宮】</note><note n="0966010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">我惟＝惟念【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0966010"><lem>我惟</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">惟念</rdg></app>老病死</l><l>三界之大患</l>
<lb n="0966a20"/><l>福盡而命終</l><l><note n="0966011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">氣絕＝棄之【三】【宮】</note><note n="0966011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">氣絕＝棄之【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0966011"><lem>氣絕</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">棄之</rdg></app>於黃泉</l>
<lb n="0966a21"/><l>身爛還為土</l><l>魂魄隨因緣</l>
<lb n="0966a22"/><l>吾用畏是故</l><l>學道昇泥洹</l></lg>
<lb n="0966a23"/><p>於是梵志<note n="0966012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔聞佛所說〕－【宮】</note><app n="0966012"><lem>聞佛所說</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。心<note n="0966013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">開＝淨【宮】</note><app n="0966013"><lem>開</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">淨</rdg></app>意解。即得道&CB00528;。
<lb n="0966a24"/><note n="0966014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">前＝長【三】【宮】</note><note n="0966014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">前＝長【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0966014"><lem>前</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">長</rdg></app><note n="0966015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受五戒＝跪受戒【宮】</note><app n="0966015"><lem>受五戒</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">跪受戒</rdg></app>。為清信士。不殺不盜不婬不欺。
<lb n="0966a25"/>奉孝不<note n="0966016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">醉＋（為佛）【宋】，（為佛作禮）【元】【明】</note><app n="0966016"><lem>醉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">醉為佛</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">醉為佛作禮</rdg></app>。歡喜而去。</p></div1>
<lb n="0966a26"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>佛說八師經</jhead></juan>
</body></text></TEI.2>
